title: patient 006, cancer, LCM [OPG study]
treatment_protocol_ch1: Tumor tissue was extracted using laser-capture microdissection.
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was extracted from tissue specimens using RNeasy kit (Qiagen, Hilden, Germany). Integrity of obtained RNA was assessed using Agilent 2100 BioAnalyzer (Agilent Technologies, Palo Alto, CA). All samples had RNA Integrity Number (RIN) greater than 5.0. Contaminant DNA was removed by digestion with RNase-free DNase (Qiagen).
label_protocol_ch1: cRNA was prepared using two-cycle target labeling and control reagents kit (Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA).
hyb_protocol: Hybridization and signal detection of HG-U133 Plus 2.0 arrays (Affymetrix) was performed following the manufacturer's instruction using the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using Affymetrix GeneChip Scanner 3000.
description: Gene expression profile of surgically resected material
data_processing: The data was normalized by robust multichip analysis (RMA) using R/Bioconductor (affy package).

title: patient 047, cancer, homogenized [OPG study]
treatment_protocol_ch1: Tumor tissue was extracted using laser-capture microdissection.
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was extracted from tissue specimens using RNeasy kit (Qiagen, Hilden, Germany). Integrity of obtained RNA was assessed using Agilent 2100 BioAnalyzer (Agilent Technologies, Palo Alto, CA). All samples had RNA Integrity Number (RIN) greater than 5.0. Contaminant DNA was removed by digestion with RNase-free DNase (Qiagen).
label_protocol_ch1: cRNA was prepared using two-cycle target labeling and control reagents kit (Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA).
hyb_protocol: Hybridization and signal detection of HG-U133 Plus 2.0 arrays (Affymetrix) was performed following the manufacturer's instruction using the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using Affymetrix GeneChip Scanner 3000.
description: Gene expression profile of surgically resected material
